<chapter id="chapter-introduction">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>This plugin provides client side support for tile based layers. It
        provides mainly helper methods to create tile based layers and has utility classes for
        OSM layers.</para>

    <section>
        <title>Plugin structure</title>

        <para>This plugin contains multiple artifacts, that are listed below:</para>

        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para><emphasis>impl</emphasis>: The basic Tile Based Layer client functionality. It
                    contains renderers for tile based layers and the OSM layer.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
                <para><emphasis>example-jar</emphasis>: Jar that contains showcase
                    examples.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
                <para><emphasis>documentation</emphasis>: This documentation.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </section>

    <section>
        <title>Dependencies</title>

        <para>Basic Tile based layer client artifact:</para>

        <programlisting>&lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.geomajas.plugin&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;geomajas-client-gwt2-plugin-tilebasedlayer&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;<?eval ${project.version}?>&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;/dependency&gt;</programlisting>
    </section>

</chapter>
